Usage: reset_annotated_delay [-help] { [-all ] |[ [-from <from_pins>] [-to <to_pins>] ]| [<object_spec>] }

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<object_spec>         # List of objects: instances, nets (string, optional)
-all                  # Specifies to remove annotated delay from all arcs
                      # (bool, optional)
-from <from_pins>     # Specifies the from pin of arc on which annotated delay
                      # is to be reset (string, optional)
-to <to_pins>         # Specifies the to pin of arc on which annotated delay is
                      # to be reset (string, optional)